<p>Wittering Surf Shop is totally committed to protecting the privacy of our site visitors and customers. The Wittering Surf Shop team are customers themselves of other Internet sites and fully appreciate and respect the importance of privacy on the Internet. We will not disclose information about our customers to third parties except where it is a necessary part of providing a service to you - e.g. Arranging for a product to be sent to you. <br />
<br />
<strong>Our Consent</strong><br />
All of our customer records are kept private, confidential and secure. Our database holds information that is collected at the time of registration, at ordering, any account modifications made by the customer. All data is collected lawfully and in accordance with the Data Protection Act 1998. We will not rent or sell your name, address, e-mail address, credit card information or personal information to any third party (excluding partners from whom you may have linked to our site) without your permission. If you have purchased from our store, subscribed to one of our newsletters and entered any of our competitions, or advised us of your e-mail address, post &amp; telephone we may occasionally update you on news and special opportunities via e-mail, &amp; post. <br />
<br />
<strong>Communication &amp; Marketing</strong><br />
By becoming a member of Wittering Surf Shop and providing us with your email, postal address, telephone number you consent to receive communication from us about our latest products and special offers (Our emails refer to your Wittering Surf Shop membership and the products &amp; services we offer including surfboards, wetsuits, clothing, accessories etc.) which we think may be of interest to you. When ordering from Wittering Surf Shop you automatically become a member. You have the ability to opt out of receiving any communication during the ordering process. <br />
<br />
<strong>Opting out of Communication</strong><br />
All Wittering Surf Shop members have the option to opt-out of receiving marketing communications from us and/or selected third parties. If you do not wish to receive marketing (emails,postal,telephone) from us and/or selected third parties we recommend you opt-out by emailing info@witteringsurfshop.com with the subject UNSUBSCRIBE. <br />
<br />
<br />
<strong>Site Statistics</strong><br />
We may disclose aggregate statistics about the number of visitors to our site or number of purchases made on the site as required by our investors. The cookies and the embedded code provide statistical information about visits to pages on the site, the duration of individual page view, paths taken by visitors through the site, data on visitors' screen settings and other general information. Wittering Surf Shop uses this type of information, as with that obtained from other cookies used on the site, to help it improve the services to its users. <br />
<br />
<strong>Checking Your Details</strong><br />
If you wish to verify the details you have submitted to Wittering Surf Shop you may do so by contacting us via the e-mail address, telephone number or address given below. Our security procedures mean that we may request proof of identity before we reveal information. This proof of identity will take the form of your e-mail address and password submitted upon registration. We would strongly recommend that you do not use the browser's password memory function as that would permit other people using your terminal to access your personal information - write it down and keep it somewhere safe. <br />
<br />
<strong>What are Cookies?</strong><br />
A cookie is a small information file that is sent to your computer and is stored on your hard drive. If you have registered with us then your computer will store an identifying cookie which will save you time each time you re-visit Wittering Surf Shop, by remembering your email address for you. You can change the settings on your browser to prevent cookies being stored on your computer without your explicit consent. <br />
<br />
<strong>Contacting Us</strong><br />
We are always pleased to hear from our customers (even if it is a complaint!). We are always grateful for any time you spend providing us with the knowledge we need to ensure our customers are completely satisfied - we want you to return to the site and to recommend us to your friends and family. If you have any questions or feedback about this statement please do not hesitate to contact a customer service member of the Wittering Surf Shop team, who will be delighted to answer any questions you may have. <br />
<br />
